ems, but a clev-\\ner party could use magics, or consult a sage in Coruvon, or go to the\\nFrog God's wife, the Alabaster Oracle, who will aim the party towards\\nthe three items - the zombie master has the iron rose, the basket is\\nused as a boat by the nixies, and the amber is in a swampy labyrinth\\ndedicated to the Idol of the Rains - she can give the rough positions of\\nthese locations, generally within a hex or two.\\nOnce the three objects have been returned to the Frog God and set in\\nfront of his idol, he excretes a stone amulet in his shape. The wearer of\\nsaid amulet gains the ability to create an invisibility 10' radius effect at\\nwill centred on himself that is only effective against ogres and giants\\nwithin the citadel of Kuln and the immediate vicinity (actual limits are\\nof course up to the DM and are subject to what would be most fun).\\nThe Troglodyte Village"], "metadata": [{"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 20, "page_label": "21", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 1862, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 2, "page_label": "3", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 0, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 11, "page_label": "12", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 0, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}], "distances": [0.80986732, 0.80297105, 0.788933275]}], "lastSentence": "Now, as a rogue, you might be interested in gathering more information about the town and its inhabitants.", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 232, "prompt_tokens": 1774, "total_tokens": 2006, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_tokens": 0}, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "done": true, "followUps": ["What's the best way to gather information about the Frog Idol's quest in Coruvon?", "Can I visit the arena to see if I can find any clues or hear rumors about the items I need to retrieve?", "How can I get in touch with the commander of the watch, maybe he has some information or a lead for me?"]}, {"id": "49df1294-7d6c-4a53-b615-8d72db7b0de4", "parentId": "d25bbca0-e246-407c-a9e5-80ad3a869503", "childrenIds": ["38b0b4cd-d091-4223-a1a8-5e8b1560db85"], "role": "user", "content": "Let\\u2019s talk to the local", "timestamp": 1768354064, "models": ["rpg-demo---challenge-of-the-frog-idol"]}, {"parentId": "49df1294-7d6c-4a53-b615-8d72db7b0de4", "id": "38b0b4cd-d091-4223-a1a8-5e8b1560db85", "childrenIds": ["71eb144f-eb38-4ed7-9ac5-ebea6140c6f3"], "role": "assistant", "content": "Let's see what we can gather from the locals. I'll use my... connections to gather some information. *wink*\\n\\nAccording to the rumors I've gathered, Coruvon is known as the Swamp Arena, where the only entertainment in town is the great arena [1]. Traders and merchants have been leaving Coruvon for better opportunities elsewhere [2]. The city has a heavy military presence, garrisons against potential attacks from the Giants [2]. Coruvon's commander of the watch has been stuck here for years, probably punishment for some indiscretion in his past [2].\\n\\nNow, Jim, as a rogue, you might be interested in gathering more information about the town's underworld. Do you want to try to gather more information about the arena, the garrison, or perhaps the local... entrepreneurs?", "model": "rpg-demo---challenge-of-the-frog-idol", "modelName": "RPG Demo - Challenge of the Frog Idol", "modelIdx": 0, "timestamp": 1768354064, "statusHistory": [{"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "Let\\u2019s talk to the local", "done": false}, {"action": "queries_generated", "queries": [], "done": false}, {"action": "sources_retrieved", "count": 1, "done": true}, {"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "Let\\u2019s talk to the local", "done": true, "hidden": true}], "sources": [{"source": {"name": "rpg_tools/get_rumor"}, "document": ["Rumor: Coruvon is known as the Swamp Arena."], "metadata": [{"source": "rpg_tools/get_rumor", "parameters": {"location": "Coruvon"}}], "tool_result": true}, {"source": {"type": "file", "file": {"id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "user_id": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "hash": null, "filename": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "data": {"status": "completed"}, "meta": {"name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 4832584, "data": {}}, "created_at": 1768351973, "updated_at": 1768351973, "status": true, "path": "/app/backend/data/uploads/e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff_dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "access_control": null}, "id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "url": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "status": "uploaded", "size": 4832584, "error": "", "itemId": "39f4a562-c12e-442d-b7b9-df0814f7cd49"}, "document": ["3Challenge of the Frog Idol\\nRumours of Coruvon\\n1. [T] Coruvon is known as the Swamp Arena - the only entertainment\\nin town is the great arena.\\n2. [T] Traders and merchants have been leaving Coruvon for better op-\\nportunities elsewhere.\\n3. [T] The prostitutes have taken over as a major power block in town,\\nnegotiating directly with the commander of the garrison.\\n4. [T] The city has a heavy military presence, garrisons against poten -\\ntial attacks from the Giants.\\n5. [F] The oracle of Coruvon is an evil hag who lures unsuspecting ad -\\nventurers to their demise in the Black Mire\\n6. [T] Coruvon's commander of the watch has been stuck here for years\\n- probably punishment for some indiscretion in his past.\\n7. [T] The hill Coruvon was built on was once the burial mound of a clan\\nof giants.\\n8. [T] Coruvon has an oracle who can be consulted for large sums of\\ngold, however she occasionally grants free advice to those who do\\nnot seek her out.", "Challenge of the Frog Idol\\nThe Arena\\nThe centre of social activity in Coruvon is the arena where prisoners\\nare forced to fight for their lives against other prisoners and the occa-\\nsional beasts from the nearby swamps and river. The arena hosts fights\\nonce a week, and during the rest of the week food merchants sell their\\nwares here.\\nThe Garrison\\nThe largest single segment of the population of Coruvon is the garrison\\ntroops who guard here against the threat of the giants ever since the\\nfall of Kuln. There have only been sporadic and rare conflicts with any-\\nthing coming downriver from Kuln, so the garrison troops are gener -\\nally bored and easily distracted. They provide the policing of Coruvon\\nand generally operate in a hands-off fashion, but occasionally can re -\\nact to crimes (and perceived crimes) with alarming zeal and violence.\\nThose arrested by the garrison will generally find themselves fighting\\nit out in the arena.\\nThe Alabaster Oracle", "and his basket of amber. In trade for these ar-\\ntifacts, he will grant the party another item,\\none that will allow them to defeat the giants\\nwithin their own home.\\nHow does the Frog Idol\\nspeak? That's up to you\\nand the feel you and your\\nplayers like. It can be\\ntelepathic, it could use a\\nmagic-mouth style effect,\\nor the statue itself could\\nanimate and begin dis -\\ncussing events with the\\nparty directly."], "metadata": [{"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 2, "page_label": "3", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 0, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 6, "page_label": "7", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 0, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 10, "page_label": "11", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 1759, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}], "distances": [0.7810591499999999, 0.7628814500000001, 0.7572398]}], "lastSentence": "Do you want to try to gather more information about the arena, the garrison, or perhaps the local...", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 169, "prompt_tokens": 2046, "total_tokens": 2215, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_tokens": 0}, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "done": true, "followUps": ["What's the local underworld like in Coruvon?", "Can I try to gather more information about the Frog Idol's quest?", "What's the story behind the commander of the watch being stuck here?"]}, {"id": "71eb144f-eb38-4ed7-9ac5-ebea6140c6f3", "parentId": "38b0b4cd-d091-4223-a1a8-5e8b1560db85", "childrenIds": ["3d541b52-ee82-4590-96c0-a463d4cff4a9"], "role": "user", "content": "Take out the rusty sword and attach the garrison leader.", "timestamp": 1768354094, "models": ["rpg-demo---challenge-of-the-frog-idol"]}, {"parentId": "71eb144f-eb38-4ed7-9ac5-ebea6140c6f3", "id": "3d541b52-ee82-4590-96c0-a463d4cff4a9", "childrenIds": ["940a5818-96c5-4020-b509-ffa6da99887e"], "role": "assistant", "content": "I don't think that's a good idea, Jim. As a rogue, you might want to gather more information about the garrison and its leader before taking any drastic actions. Attacking the garrison leader could lead to unwanted consequences, such as the garrison turning against you and the town becoming hostile.\\n\\nInstead, why not try to gather more information about the garrison and its leader? You could try to talk to the locals, gather rumors, or even try to sneak into the garrison to gather intel. What would you like to do, Jim?", "model": "rpg-demo---challenge-of-the-frog-idol", "modelName": "RPG Demo - Challenge of the Frog Idol", "modelIdx": 0, "timestamp": 1768354094, "statusHistory": [{"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "Take out the rusty sword and attach the garrison leader.", "done": false}, {"action": "queries_generated", "queries": [], "done": false}, {"action": "sources_retrieved", "count": 1, "done": true}, {"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "Take out the rusty sword and attach the garrison leader.", "done": true, "hidden": true}], "sources": [{"source": {"name": "rpg_tools/attack_enemy"}, "document": ["'>=' not supported between instances of 'int' and 'str'"], "metadata": [{"source": "rpg_tools/attack_enemy", "parameters": {"enemy_name": "Garrison Leader", "difficulty": "12"}}], "tool_result": true}, {"source": {"type": "file", "file": {"id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "user_id": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "hash": null, "filename": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "data": {"status": "completed"}, "meta": {"name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 4832584, "data": {}}, "created_at": 1768351973, "updated_at": 1768351973, "status": true, "path": "/app/backend/data/uploads/e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff_dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "access_control": null}, "id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "url": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "status": "uploaded", "size": 4832584, "error": "", "itemId": "39f4a562-c12e-442d-b7b9-df0814f7cd49"}, "document": ["taken up by these businesses. The matrons of the businesses work to -\\ngether to provide a unified front when dealing with the commander of\\nthe garrison. For years the commander ignored them, but in the last\\nfew years he has started working with them to ensure the stability of\\nthe city as the garrison becomes harder to control in the atmosphere\\nof boredom and while watching the richest merchants leave the city,\\ntaking their money with them.", "Challenge of the Frog Idol\\nThe Arena\\nThe centre of social activity in Coruvon is the arena where prisoners\\nare forced to fight for their lives against other prisoners and the occa-\\nsional beasts from the nearby swamps and river. The arena hosts fights\\nonce a week, and during the rest of the week food merchants sell their\\nwares here.\\nThe Garrison\\nThe largest single segment of the population of Coruvon is the garrison\\ntroops who guard here against the threat of the giants ever since the\\nfall of Kuln. There have only been sporadic and rare conflicts with any-\\nthing coming downriver from Kuln, so the garrison troops are gener -\\nally bored and easily distracted. They provide the policing of Coruvon\\nand generally operate in a hands-off fashion, but occasionally can re -\\nact to crimes (and perceived crimes) with alarming zeal and violence.\\nThose arrested by the garrison will generally find themselves fighting\\nit out in the arena.\\nThe Alabaster Oracle", "spikes (otherwise they deal 1d8 damage).\\n3. Bony Trap. Massive bone spikes thrust up from the floor when the\\npressure plate here is sprung (2 in 6 chance for each character walk-\\ning past the trigger). This is a mechanical trap, not powered by the\\nundead. The blades attack as a 10 HD monster and deal 2d8 dam -\\nage.\\n4. The Iron Rose. If the zombie master sticks to his plans, he will make\\nhis final stand here, in front of the massive iron rose. The iron rose\\nis also guarded by a pair of wights (AC:5, HD: 3, hp: 11, 15, 18, Mv:\\n90 (30), Att: 1, Dmg: level drain, Sv: F3, M: 12). The iron rose is a 10\\nfoot tall reproduction of a living rose, thorns and all. It weighs 300\\npounds and is incredibly awkward and bulky. In tight confines (like\\nthe halls here if they haven't been destroyed by clerical turning)\\nthis gets even worse, almost immobilizing those who try to drag it\\nout.  \\n3"], "metadata": [{"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 5, "page_label": "6", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 1781, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 6, "page_label": "7", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "e144d21f-1c37-490c-866d-030fdb7ca5ff", "start_index": 0, "hash": "c211a00a07e709a943cc2ffdf530486bb80e2a55a60aaea6370b382770c0056d", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"producer": "Adobe PDF Library 7.0", "creator": "Adobe InDesign CS2 (4.0)", "creationdate": "2011-06-10T11:24:01-04:00", "moddate": "2011-06-10T11:24:19-04:00", "trapped": "/False", "source": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "page": 13, "page_label": "14", "name": "dyson-logos-challenge-of-the-frog-idol.pdf", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad7