": 1768337788, "user": {"id": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "name": "Pluto System", "role": "admin", "email": "system@pluto.local"}, "write_access": true, "type": "collection"}, "document": ["Using systems design methodologies to manage complex sociotechnical systems is a well-known and well-published domain of engineering science.\\nAlign human and technical elements using systems design principles and tools\\nUse Info-Tech's methodology to align the human and technical elements of your innovative Gen AI solutions.\\nIdentify the human or organizational need.\\nDecompose solutions requirements with human and technical lenses.\\nDescribe the human-technology interaction.\\nWhat is a design methodology?\\nInfo-Tech's sociotechnical wireframe methodology for AI solutions\\nDescribe the human or organizational need for the solution.\\nInfo-Tech Insight\\nDesign solutions with a sociotechnical lens.\\nConsider not only the technology but also the social systems within which the solution will be embedded to manage requirements and constraints.\\nUse the human-tech ladder to define the solution requirements and constraints.", "Describe the human or organizational need for the solution.\\nFrame unknowns and challenges as learning objectives.\\nUse the human-tech ladder to define the solution requirements and constraints.\\nCreate innovative Gen AI solutions\\nArchitect the solution at the human-tech intersection.\\nDevelop the human-technology story\\nDocument the human-technology experience.\\nBreak down the technical components.\\nTell the human-technology story.\\nMap out human activities and technology functions.\\nList human activities involved in using the system.\\nMap human activities to specific technology functions to describe how technology supports or enhances human activities.\\nUse a flowchart or use cases (or other techniques) to describe the intended interactions between users and technology.\\nInclude decision points, loops, and conditional paths that reflect human-technology interactions.", "Info-Tech's adaptation of the human-tech ladder decomposes AI solutions into their social and technological components to emphasize and manage the complexity of integrating AI systems within social and technical contexts. The modified ladder introduces layers specifically dedicated to AI, data, software, and hardware to help development a wholistic understanding of solution requirements involving AI.\\nThe human-tech ladder can help you systematically consider both the social (human) and technical challenges at each stage of solution design and technology implementation to ensure a more holistic and integrated approach to developing complex sociotechnical systems.\\nLeverage the human-tech ladder to deliver great solutions\\nWhy use the human-tech ladder?"], "metadata": [{"source": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "name": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "a5803090-e721-40b6-844d-6d59276812ad", "start_index": 0, "hash": "7762d309fb9ba73f96d122afab7ecc11bd4a81dc2ba6e722bd61671edaa395bb", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"source": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "name": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "a5803090-e721-40b6-844d-6d59276812ad", "start_index": 0, "hash": "7762d309fb9ba73f96d122afab7ecc11bd4a81dc2ba6e722bd61671edaa395bb", "embedding_config": {"engine": "ollama", "model": "nomic-embed-text"}}, {"source": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "name": "it-Wireframe-Your-Generative-AI-Solution-Design-Storyboard.pptx", "created_by": "e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9", "file_id": "a5803090-e721-40b6-844d-6d59276812ad", "start_index": 0, "hash": "7762d309fb9ba73f96d122afab7ecc11bd4a8