for a large sum of gold. [3]\\n\\n5. When traveling through the Black Mire, be sure to check if you are on the \\"Causeway\\" or in the \\"Swamp\\" itself, as this may affect any encounters you have. [2]\\n\\nLet me know if you have any other questions, Grom! I'm here to help guide you through your adventure in the Black Mire.", "model": "rpg-demo---challenge-of-the-frog-idol", "modelName": "RPG Demo - Challenge of the Frog Idol", "modelIdx": 0, "timestamp": 1768352156, "statusHistory": [{"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "I am Grom the Barbarian", "done": false}, {"action": "queries_generated", "queries": ["Grom the Barbarian", "Barbarian character archetypes", "RPG character classes"], "done": false}, {"action": "sources_retrieved", "count": 1, "done": true}, {"action": "knowledge_search", "query": "I am Grom the Barbarian", "done": true, "hidden": true}], "embeds": ["\\n            <!doctype html>\\n            <html lang=\\"en\\">\\n            <head>\\n                <meta charset=\\"utf-8\\">\\n                <meta name=\\"viewport\\" content=\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\">\\n                <style>\\n                    :root {\\n                        --bg-color: #ffffff;\\n                        --text-color: #1f2937;\\n                        --accent-color: #2563eb;\\n                        --border-color: #e5e7eb;\\n                        --danger: #dc2626;\\n                        --gold: #d97706;\\n                        --purple: #7c3aed;\\n                    }\\n                    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\n                    \\n                    body {\\n                        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\"Segoe UI\\", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\\n                        background-color: var(--bg-color);\\n                        color: var(--text-color);\\n                        margin: 0;\\n                        padding: 0;\\n                        width: 100%;       /* Full W