perience included responsibility as a security officer for Toronto Dominion Bank, Blackberry, The ATCO Group, and Info-Tech Research Group.\\n\\n\\n\\nMichel\\n\\nMichel H\\u00e9bert, PhD, is the Practice Lead for the Industry Research Group at Info-Tech Research Group. As an analyst, Michel specializes in security, privacy, and emerging technologies. He helps clients navigate industry-specific challenges, enhance their security practices, and develop strategies for emerging technologies. Recently, he has focused on the impact of AI, machine learning, and quantum computing on cybersecurity.\\n\\n\\n\\nValence\\n\\nValence Howden is an International Speaker, Advisory Fellow and Distinguished Analyst at Infotech Research Group with over 30 years of experience in optimizing organizations through improving their governance, strategies, operating models and risk management practices.\\n\\nValence is a 2023 and 2024 HDI Top 25 thought leader in service management and is the Standards Council of Canada chair \\u2013 and ISO voting member and delegate for Canada - for IT Governance, Service Management and Business Process Management."}	1768148939	/app/backend/data/uploads/ddd64263-ee23-4a61-b60e-251aed34c4b6_notes.docx	null
