03a53175-1c6c-4e23-aca2-f837847c7221	e92fa032-845e-4ce9-ad71-3810ca14f7a9	Bio and Sample Initiatives.pptx	{"name": "Bio and Sample Initiatives.pptx", "content_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.presentationml.presentation", "size": 10520210, "data": {"knowledge_id": "adbeade6-cb53-42c9-88cc-adf0f39ec6df"}, "collection_name": "adbeade6-cb53-42c9-88cc-adf0f39ec6df"}	1768337812	39b48beea110d50915cdef43ad838cb0cc9f3ca6db63807fdb501553f5db0f82	{"status": "completed", "content": "I do research in Technology Services and provide Technical Counseling for Cloud Infrastructure Teams.\\n\\nI'm a Systems Engineer and my passion is complex sociotechnical systems. \\n\\nDr. Justin St-Maurice\\n\\nPrincipal Research Director\\n\\nTechnology Services\\n\\nInfo-Tech Research Group\\n\\nI spent 9 years teaching Health Informatics and Information Systems at a community college in Ontario.\\n\\nI have my Solution Developer, Solution Architect and Data Analytics certifications from AWS.\\n\\n\\n\\nCloud Apps are different.\\n\\nInfo-Tech Services\\n\\nWHAT'S THE CHALLENGE?\\n\\nHOW CAN WE HELP?\\n\\nDeveloping cloud apps isn't an evolution; it's a reinvention. It's not just taking UIs and database and putting them online. It's a new way of thinking about problems and solutions.\\n\\nHost a 2-day workshop with the Cloud Engineering Team:\\n\\nConfigure development environments.\\n\\nCreate new modules.\\n\\nDevelop core documentation .\\n\\nHost an enterprise workshop to develop internal training:\\n\\nReview current developer baseline competencies.\\n\\nIdentify requirements and learning outcomes.\\n\\nCreate workshop material for internal delivery.\\n\\nDeliver a 'trial' workshop to refine content.\\n\\nPeople need to learn how to use the tools. Developing modern web apps requires familiarity with Azure, Terraform, VS Code, GitHub, and benefits from standard DevOps processes.\\n\\nPeople need to know how to build with modules. Modules are  the 'material' for scalable solutions and need to be incorporated into the core design.\\n\\nHOW CAN WE HELP LATER?\\n\\nPeople aren't going to take the plunge alone. You won't get a critical mass of cloud-ready developers from your pool without systematically deploying a professional development program.\\n\\nFacilitate an enterprise hackathon:\\n\\nBuild practical web app development skills.\\n\\nCreate prototypes and proofs of concept.\\n\\nBuild capacity and engagement.\\n\\nSAMPLE ENGAGEMENT\\n\\n\\n\\nStart your cloud journey.\\n\\nInfo-Tech Technical Counselor\\n\\nUNLOCK NEW OPPORTUNITES WITH CLOUD NATIVE BUSINESS CAPABILITIES.\\n\\nSEAT HOLDER SUPPORT\\n\\nTalent Development: Hands-on support to rapidly understand cloud technologies and prepare team for certifications and in-house development with infrastructure as code concepts and CICD pipelines.\\n\\nCloud Proof of Concept: Onsite visit to create a customized proof of concept for a document management system. \\n\\nStakeholder Engagement: Leverage best practice resources and experts in infrastructure and security to work with internal stakeholders and ensure the foundation is in place for scalable, secure solutions.\\n\\nValue assessment: Explore opportunities and cost of ownership  while 'future proofing' skillsets and capabilities.\\n\\nDeveloping cloud apps isn't an evolution; it's a reinvention. It's not just taking UIs and database and putting them online. It's a new way of thinking about problems and solutions.\\n\\nPeople need to learn how to use the tools. Developing modern web apps requires familiarity with Azure, Terraform, VS Code, GitHub, and benefits from standard DevOps processes.\\n\\nPeople need to know how to build with services and modules. Modules are the building blocks for scalable solutions and need to be incorporated into the core design.\\n\\nPeople aren't going to take the plunge alone. You won't get a critical mass of cloud-ready talent without systematically deploying a professional development program.\\n\\nQUOTE\\n\\n\\"I don't know what happened when you worked with Jackson a month ago, but he's on a different level now. Something clicked. He's running his first major project and he's running laps around everybody else in IT.\\"\\n\\nSAMPLE ENGAGEMENT"}	1768337816	/app/backend/data/uploads/03a53175-1c6c-4e23-aca2-f837847c7221_Bio and Sample Initiatives.pptx	null
