alysis, and teaching informatics at the postsecondary level. Outside of work, Justin is a certified ACC coach, Vice-President of the Guelph Hiking Trail Club, a cellist in the Cambridge Symphony Orchestra, and an aspiring curler at the Guelph Curling Club.\\n\\nTalk to someone you know, who knows you well\\n\\nYour Technical Counselor will:\\n\\nBecome intimately familiar with the details of your role and organization\\n\\nExpertly guide you, and your team, through your biggest challenges and major projects\\n\\nHelp you customize your annual Key Initiative Plan to maximize IT performance\\n\\nDirect you to the most relevant research, resources, content, and experiences\\n\\nSchedule regular check-ins with you to discuss progress and next steps\\n\\nAct as an industry peer and confidant to discuss challenges and opportunities\\n\\nInfo-Tech Publication & Keynotes:\\n\\nBring AI Out of the Shadows\\n\\nGet Ready to Deliver AI Services\\n\\nLeverage Metrics and Benchmarks to Evaluate LLMs\\n\\nWireframe Your Generative AI Solution Design\\n\\nTransform Your Professional Services Organization With a Tech-Enabled Digital Business Strategy\\n\\nPeer-Reviewed Publications:\\n\\nUsing cognitive work analysis to compare complex system domains\\n\\nModeling patient treatment with medical records: An abstraction hierarchy to understand user competencies and needs. \\n\\nAn exploratory case study to understand primary care users and their data quality tradeoffs\\n\\nAnalyzing primary care data to characterize inappropriate emergency room use"}	1768337817	/app/backend/data/uploads/c40674b6-86ca-44fb-942b-3cb98d7f73f9_Justin St-Maurice - Bio.pptx	null
