of of concept for a document management system. \\n\\u2713 Stakeholder Engagement: Leverage best practice \\nresources and experts in infrastructure and security to \\nwork with internal stakeholders and ensure the foundation \\nis in place for scalable, secure solutions.\\n\\u2713 Value assessment: Explore opportunities and cost of \\nownership  while 'future proofing' skillsets and capabilities.\\nQ U O T E\\n\\"I don't know what happened when you worked with \\nJackson a month ago, but he's on a different level now. \\nSomething clicked. He's running his first major project \\nand he's running laps around everybody else in IT.\\"\\nStart your cloud journey.\\nSAMPLE ENGAGEMENT"}	1768337853	/app/backend/data/uploads/d8e0d0f4-248a-4ca6-95da-93bae1209736_Justin TC Bio and Sample Projects - Copy.pdf	null
